description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Health Education England&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Health Education England is at the core of the NHS’s £5 billion investment into education and training across the NHS. We’re working to build a modern, user-led, digital training system that works more simply for its users and we’re looking for talented people to help us achieve this goal. The successful candidate will be a Full Stack Developer with a passion for personal development. They will be joining a multidisciplinary team, contributing their own experience and adding value whilst collaborating with others and potentially mentoring colleagues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We don’t expect you to know everything. The team is very happy to help with any areas you may have had little exposure to, but we do require a certain level of experience and the right underlying learning attitude. We encourage personal development and encourage our team members grow alongside our digital solutions, helping make the NHS bette&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;r.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We heavily use the following tools and technologies:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Java for our back-end services&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Angular and React for our front-end applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;MySQL, MSSQL, MongoDB&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Elasticsearch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You should apply if:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You enjoy working as part of a multidisciplinary team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You are an experienced in ideally one or more of the following programming languages Java, Scala, JavaScript and MVW frameworks (we use Angular)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You have a good working knowledge of software design principles.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You have the ability to research and learn new programming tools and techniques.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You have an understanding of version control (we use Git).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You have experience working on, or with web technologies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You have a strong knowledge of databases, web performance and web security&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Agile experience in a development environment is not required, but an understanding of agile and ability to think agile is required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Benefits:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Flexible working hours. Whether it’s home, remotely, working part-time, working compressed hours. We’ve got people doing it and we’re happy to discuss options with you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Training and learning opportunities. Many of our staff attend and run conferences and meetups.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;An NHS Pension.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bike loans and season ticket loans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discounts at major high street stores including Nandos, Tossed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maternity leave, adoption and shared parental leave.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skills:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Java (8,11) for our back-end services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Angular9for our front-end applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;React&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MySQL, MSSQL &amp; MongoDB&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Elasticsearch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ops/Collaboration:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AWS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Git&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agile thinker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keen pair programmer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Desirable:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skills:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;REST - general knowledge of web services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spring or SpringBoot&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Junit, Mockito and TDD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ELK Stack (Elasticsearch, Logstash, Kibana)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;JavaScript (ES6 Typescript)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Npm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Jasmine and Karma&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Protractor, Cucumber and Gherkin&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ops/Collaboration:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Jenkins, Ansible and Docker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maven, Gradle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Terraform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scrum experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy teaching and learning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;JIRA and Confluence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants will commence at the bottom of Band 7 with a full-time starting salary of £38,890, with pay step increases after 2 years’ service and 5 years’ service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These salaries are offered in accordance with NHS Terms and Conditions and the HEE Pay Progression Policy and are subject to annual cost of living review.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you like what you have read and think you have the skills and experience we need then don&#39;t delay, apply today! We get lots of applications for our roles and so we sometimes have to close our posts early. Don&#39;t miss out!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Simon Meredith&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Head of Software Development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: simon.meredith@hee.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
